# Title: Outgoing Logon with New Credentials
# Author: Max Altgelt (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-04-06
# Level: low
# Description: Detects logon events that specify new credentials
# MITRE Tactic: Lateral Movement
# Tags: attack.lateral-movement, attack.t1550
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/account_management/win_security_susp_logon_newcredentials.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate remote administration activity

EventID=4624 LogonType=9